293
00:13:44,448 --> 00:13:48,202
<c.japanese>&lrm;あの闇 見た目どおりの
&lrm;まずさじゃねえか</c.japanese>

294
00:13:50,621 --> 00:13:52,289
<c.japanese>&lrm;こりゃ 売れねえな</c.japanese>

295
00:13:52,373 --> 00:13:53,207
<c.japanese>&lrm;ん？</c.japanese>

296
00:13:54,375 --> 00:13:58,003
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）勝っておきながら
&lrm;殺さないとは どういう了見だ？</c.japanese>

297
00:13:58,087 --> 00:14:01,006
<c.japanese>&lrm;もう一度 戦い 必ず殺せ</c.japanese>

298
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,384
<c.japanese>&lrm;本気か？</c.japanese>

299
00:14:04,009 --> 00:14:08,389
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）妹の命 我々が
&lrm;握っていることを忘れるな</c.japanese>

300
00:14:11,851 --> 00:14:12,893
<c.japanese>（斬蔵）まずっ</c.japanese>

301
00:14:15,729 --> 00:14:18,399
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）う～ 腰痛(いて)え</c.japanese>

302
00:14:18,482 --> 00:14:21,777
<c.japanese>&lrm;ったく…
&lrm;水くみ まき割り 掃除に⸺</c.japanese>

303
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:24,697
<c.japanese>&lrm;どんだけ人使い荒いんだよ
&lrm;（灼岩）ハハ…</c.japanese>

304
00:14:25,489 --> 00:14:27,324
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たまのあくび）
&lrm;（灼岩･真介）ん？</c.japanese>

305
00:14:27,408 --> 00:14:28,826
<c.japanese>&lrm;迅火は？</c.japanese>

306
00:14:28,909 --> 00:14:29,785
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）あれ？</c.japanese>

307
00:14:29,869 --> 00:14:32,705
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）そういえば
&lrm;さっき 出てったっすけど…</c.japanese>

308
00:14:32,788 --> 00:14:33,789
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）ん…</c.japanese>

309
00:14:38,544 --> 00:14:40,546
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）&lrm;雷堂斬蔵…</c.japanese>

310
00:14:43,883 --> 00:14:46,176
<c.japanese>&lrm;あれが 人間…</c.japanese>

311
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:49,930
<c.japanese>&lrm;よかったな 命があって</c.japanese>

312
00:14:51,682 --> 00:14:52,808
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）んっ…</c.japanese>

313
00:14:58,022 --> 00:14:59,189
<c.japanese>&lrm;はっ！</c.japanese>

314
00:14:59,273 --> 00:15:00,274
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）きゃあっ！</c.japanese>

315
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:05,279
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ いや… あっ…</c.japanese>

316
00:15:06,113 --> 00:15:07,781
<c.japanese>&lrm;灼岩？</c.japanese>

317
00:15:09,450 --> 00:15:10,659
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）何の用ですか？</c.japanese>

318
00:15:11,285 --> 00:15:13,871
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）ご飯できてるから
&lrm;呼びに来たんす</c.japanese>

319
00:15:13,954 --> 00:15:14,788
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）いりません</c.japanese>

320
00:15:14,872 --> 00:15:18,292
<c.japanese>&lrm;育ち盛りなんだから
&lrm;食べなきゃダメっす</c.japanese>

321
00:15:18,375 --> 00:15:20,252
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）あっち行ってなさい</c.japanese>

322
00:15:22,463 --> 00:15:24,048
<c.japanese>&lrm;たま様から聞いたっす</c.japanese>

323
00:15:25,090 --> 00:15:27,551
<c.japanese>&lrm;生きてて よかったじゃないっすか</c.japanese>

324
00:15:28,177 --> 00:15:29,678
<c.japanese>&lrm;生きてるんす</c.japanese>

325
00:15:29,762 --> 00:15:32,306
<c.japanese>&lrm;生きてれば きっと
&lrm;いいことあるっす</c.japanese>

326
00:15:33,140 --> 00:15:36,352
<c.japanese>&lrm;あなたは 生きてて
&lrm;いいことなんて あったんですか？</c.japanese>

327
00:15:36,435 --> 00:15:41,065
<c.japanese>&lrm;村で迫害され 親に売られ
&lrm;半分 闇に改造されて</c.japanese>

328
00:15:41,148 --> 00:15:43,734
<c.japanese>&lrm;たま様に会えました</c.japanese>

329
00:15:43,817 --> 00:15:47,071
<c.japanese>&lrm;迅火様や真介様にも会えました</c.japanese>

330
00:15:48,656 --> 00:15:49,490
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）ふむ…</c.japanese>

331
00:15:49,573 --> 00:15:51,825
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）ほら ご飯 行くっすよ
&lrm;（迅火）んっ おあっ…</c.japanese>

332
00:15:51,909 --> 00:15:52,826
<c.japanese>&lrm;（錫杖(しゃくじょう)の音）</c.japanese>

333
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:54,328
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩･迅火）あ…</c.japanese>

334
00:15:56,413 --> 00:15:58,624
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）え？
&lrm;（迅火）断怪衆？</c.japanese>

335
00:15:58,707 --> 00:15:59,833
<c.japanese>&lrm;なぜ ここに…</c.japanese>

336
00:15:59,917 --> 00:16:02,086
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）調べなど いくらでもつく</c.japanese>

337
00:16:03,796 --> 00:16:04,797
<c.japanese>&lrm;受け取れ</c.japanese>

338
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:05,714
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）んっ…</c.japanese>

339
00:16:06,757 --> 00:16:07,966
<c.japanese>果たし状？</c.japanese>

340
00:16:08,050 --> 00:16:09,635
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）もう一度</c.japanese>

341
00:16:09,718 --> 00:16:12,888
<c.japanese>&lrm;今度は 死を懸けて
&lrm;雷堂斬蔵と立ち合え</c.japanese>

342
00:16:12,971 --> 00:16:14,098
<c.japanese>&lrm;山戸(やまと)&lrm;迅火</c.japanese>

343
00:16:15,599 --> 00:16:18,102
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）逃げたら 山戸家を潰す</c.japanese>

344
00:16:18,185 --> 00:16:21,105
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）そんな脅し
&lrm;効くと思ってるんですか？</c.japanese>

345
00:16:21,188 --> 00:16:23,399
<c.japanese>&lrm;私にとって 山戸家など とっくに…</c.japanese>

346
00:16:23,482 --> 00:16:24,984
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）フッフッフ…
&lrm;（迅火）ん？</c.japanese>

347
00:16:25,693 --> 00:16:29,113
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）貴様を捨てた山戸を
&lrm;潰すか許すか⸺</c.japanese>

348
00:16:29,196 --> 00:16:31,198
<c.japanese>&lrm;自分で決めたくはないか？</c.japanese>

349
00:16:31,281 --> 00:16:32,116
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）んっ…</c.japanese>

350
00:16:32,199 --> 00:16:34,618
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）&lrm;山戸家？</c.japanese>

351
00:16:34,702 --> 00:16:36,954
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）難しく考えるな</c.japanese>

352
00:16:37,037 --> 00:16:40,874
<c.japanese>&lrm;“脅しとは ひきょうだぞ”と
&lrm;言っておけばいいのだ</c.japanese>

353
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:44,753
<c.japanese>&lrm;おのれ 断怪衆！
&lrm;脅しとは ひきょうだぞ！</c.japanese>

354
00:16:44,837 --> 00:16:46,046
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）うるさい</c.japanese>

355
00:16:46,130 --> 00:16:47,256
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）立たないでください</c.japanese>

356
00:16:47,339 --> 00:16:48,674
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）行儀悪いっすよ</c.japanese>

357
00:16:48,757 --> 00:16:50,884
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）あれ？　んん…</c.japanese>

358
00:16:50,968 --> 00:16:54,763
<c.japanese>&lrm;で その灼岩が聞いた
&lrm;山戸家とかいうのは 何だ？</c.japanese>

359
00:16:55,597 --> 00:16:56,724
<c.japanese>&lrm;んん…</c.japanese>

360
00:16:56,807 --> 00:16:58,475
<c.japanese>&lrm;返事しろよ！</c.japanese>

361
00:16:58,559 --> 00:16:59,977
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）迅火の生家だ
&lrm;（真介）あっ</c.japanese>

362
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:01,228
<c.japanese>&lrm;生家？</c.japanese>

363
00:17:01,311 --> 00:17:04,273
<c.japanese>&lrm;いちいち反応しないでください
&lrm;うっとうしい</c.japanese>

364
00:17:05,023 --> 00:17:07,526
<c.japanese>&lrm;生まれて すぐ
&lrm;師匠に引き取られたので</c.japanese>

365
00:17:07,609 --> 00:17:08,652
<c.japanese>&lrm;関わりはありません</c.japanese>

366
00:17:08,736 --> 00:17:11,822
<c.japanese>&lrm;だからって
&lrm;無視するわけにもいかんだろ</c.japanese>

367
00:17:11,905 --> 00:17:14,158
<c.japanese>&lrm;父親も母親もいるんだろ？</c.japanese>

368
00:17:14,241 --> 00:17:16,160
<c.japanese>&lrm;家は大事にしろ</c.japanese>

369
00:17:16,243 --> 00:17:19,538
<c.japanese>&lrm;すがすがしいくらいに
&lrm;まっとうなやつだな お前は</c.japanese>

370
00:17:19,621 --> 00:17:21,665
<c.japanese>&lrm;何だよ バカにすんな！</c.japanese>

371
00:17:21,749 --> 00:17:24,209
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）そんなことないっすよ
&lrm;かっこいいっす</c.japanese>

372
00:17:24,293 --> 00:17:27,046
<c.japanese>&lrm;そ… そう？　ヘヘヘ… ん？</c.japanese>

373
00:17:28,255 --> 00:17:30,549
<c.japanese>&lrm;迅火 お前は どうしたい？</c.japanese>

374
00:17:34,845 --> 00:17:37,556
<c.japanese>&lrm;山戸家に興味はありませんが</c.japanese>

375
00:17:37,639 --> 00:17:39,683
<c.japanese>&lrm;人間に負けたままなど…</c.japanese>

376
00:17:40,559 --> 00:17:41,935
<c.japanese>&lrm;我慢ならない</c.japanese>

377
00:17:42,519 --> 00:17:44,104
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ…</c.japanese>

378
00:17:44,188 --> 00:17:45,689
<c.japanese>&lrm;そうか</c.japanese>

379
00:17:59,536 --> 00:18:01,079
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）ぐっ…</c.japanese>

380
00:18:01,163 --> 00:18:03,457
<c.japanese>&lrm;違う 勝った場面を…</c.japanese>

381
00:18:04,291 --> 00:18:05,459
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ…</c.japanese>

382
00:18:21,058 --> 00:18:22,476
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）んん…
&lrm;（灼岩）ああ…</c.japanese>

383
00:18:27,898 --> 00:18:29,233
<c.japanese>&lrm;さようなら</c.japanese>

384
00:18:30,526 --> 00:18:31,735
<c.japanese>&lrm;あばよ</c.japanese>

385
00:18:38,367 --> 00:18:39,993
<c.japanese>&lrm;あ～あ…</c.japanese>

386
00:18:40,077 --> 00:18:41,161
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）くっ…</c.japanese>

387
00:18:41,245 --> 00:18:44,248
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）&lrm;その瞬間
&lrm;選択の失敗に気付いた</c.japanese>

388
00:18:44,331 --> 00:18:45,833
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）んっ</c.japanese>

389
00:18:45,916 --> 00:18:47,251
<c.japanese>&lrm;ふんっ ふっ…</c.japanese>

390
00:18:50,838 --> 00:18:54,258
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）&lrm;もはや 得物の
&lrm;小回りの問題などではなく…</c.japanese>

391
00:18:54,341 --> 00:18:56,134
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）はああっ！</c.japanese>

392
00:18:57,594 --> 00:19:01,265
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）&lrm;相手に合わせた時点で
&lrm;のまれていたのだ</c.japanese>

393
00:19:01,348 --> 00:19:02,349
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）ふんっ</c.japanese>

394
00:19:02,432 --> 00:19:03,600
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）&lrm;死ん…</c.japanese>

395
00:19:11,275 --> 00:19:15,195
<c.japanese>&lrm;うわああああああっ！</c.japanese>

396
00:19:17,531 --> 00:19:18,824
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）なっ… に!?</c.japanese>

397
00:19:19,408 --> 00:19:20,576
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ</c.japanese>

398
00:19:27,082 --> 00:19:30,586
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）フッフフ… フフフフフ…</c.japanese>

399
00:19:31,503 --> 00:19:33,589
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）うっ ああ…</c.japanese>

400
00:19:33,672 --> 00:19:35,841
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）クッ フフフ…</c.japanese>

401
00:19:35,924 --> 00:19:39,761
<c.japanese>&lrm;いざとなると
&lrm;らしさが出るものですね</c.japanese>

402
00:19:39,845 --> 00:19:42,598
<c.japanese>&lrm;今ので やっと目が覚めましたよ</c.japanese>

403
00:19:42,681 --> 00:19:45,601
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）うっ うう… ヒヒヒ…</c.japanese>

404
00:19:45,684 --> 00:19:49,313
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）さあ 続きをしましょう</c.japanese>

405
00:19:49,396 --> 00:19:50,606
<c.japanese>&lrm;本番です</c.japanese>

406
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:55,110
<c.japanese>&lrm;本番だ？　フッフフフ…</c.japanese>

407
00:19:55,193 --> 00:19:57,988
<c.japanese>&lrm;うっ… 終わりだ バカ</c.japanese>

408
00:19:58,071 --> 00:19:59,239
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）へっ？</c.japanese>

409
00:19:59,323 --> 00:20:02,618
<c.japanese>&lrm;もう動けねえよ 俺の負けだ</c.japanese>

410
00:20:03,911 --> 00:20:06,580
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）フッフフ… フハッ…</c.japanese>

411
00:20:06,663 --> 00:20:09,750
<c.japanese>&lrm;ハハハハハ… ハハハハハ…</c.japanese>

412
00:20:09,833 --> 00:20:14,379
<c.japanese>&lrm;どうだ！　どうだ 人間！
&lrm;私の勝ちだ！</c.japanese>

413
00:20:14,463 --> 00:20:17,215
<c.japanese>&lrm;な… なんてやつ…</c.japanese>

414
00:20:17,299 --> 00:20:18,133
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）フゥ…</c.japanese>

415
00:20:18,217 --> 00:20:19,760
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）あっ 大丈夫っすか？
&lrm;（真介）ん？</c.japanese>

416
00:20:20,761 --> 00:20:22,471
<c.japanese>&lrm;怖かった</c.japanese>

417
00:20:22,554 --> 00:20:25,766
<c.japanese>&lrm;おれは また
&lrm;大事なものを失うかと…</c.japanese>

418
00:20:25,849 --> 00:20:28,268
<c.japanese>&lrm;大丈夫っすよ たま様</c.japanese>

419
00:20:28,352 --> 00:20:33,273
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）ハァ ハァ ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

420
00:20:33,357 --> 00:20:35,859
<c.japanese>&lrm;ハァ…</c.japanese>

421
00:20:35,943 --> 00:20:36,777
<c.japanese>&lrm;殺(や)&lrm;れや</c.japanese>

422
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:37,861
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ</c.japanese>

423
00:20:38,487 --> 00:20:40,155
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）殺れよ</c.japanese>

424
00:20:40,239 --> 00:20:42,282
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）フッ… 断ります</c.japanese>

425
00:20:42,366 --> 00:20:44,034
<c.japanese>&lrm;あ？</c.japanese>

426
00:20:45,953 --> 00:20:49,790
<c.japanese>&lrm;よかったですね 命があって</c.japanese>

427
00:20:53,543 --> 00:20:55,921
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）フッ… 青いねえ</c.japanese>

428
00:20:56,004 --> 00:20:59,007
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）ふっ… よくやった</c.japanese>

429
00:20:59,091 --> 00:20:59,925
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）姉上…</c.japanese>

430
00:21:00,509 --> 00:21:02,427
<c.japanese>&lrm;さすが おれの迅火だ</c.japanese>

431
00:21:02,511 --> 00:21:04,930
<c.japanese>&lrm;（迅火）フッ… そりゃ もう</c.japanese>

432
00:21:05,013 --> 00:21:07,683
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）迅火様 すごかったっす</c.japanese>

433
00:21:07,766 --> 00:21:11,561
<c.japanese>&lrm;まったく とんでもねえやつだな
&lrm;おめえはよ！</c.japanese>

434
00:21:11,645 --> 00:21:13,939
<c.japanese>&lrm;みんな お前の無事を願っていた</c.japanese>

435
00:21:14,022 --> 00:21:14,940
<c.japanese>&lrm;（灼岩）フフッ</c.japanese>

436
00:21:15,023 --> 00:21:15,941
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）イヒヒッ</c.japanese>

437
00:21:16,608 --> 00:21:20,821
<c.japanese>&lrm;（たま）どうだ？
&lrm;人間の友も悪くなかろう</c.japanese>

438
00:21:20,904 --> 00:21:23,323
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

439
00:21:23,407 --> 00:21:24,574
<c.japanese>&lrm;（僧侶）立てるか？</c.japanese>

440
00:21:24,658 --> 00:21:27,744
<c.japanese>&lrm;（斬蔵）ハァ…
&lrm;見りゃ分かるだろ？　ハァ…</c.japanese>

441
00:21:27,828 --> 00:21:32,332
<c.japanese>&lrm;それより 妹は… 氷乃(ひの)はどうなる？</c.japanese>

442
00:21:33,417 --> 00:21:36,211
